                                            <h5>
                                                <b>ABSENCE FROM EXAMINATION:</b>
                                            </h5>
                                            <ol>
                                                <p>
                                                    NB: An application by the student, or if he is incapacitated, by a
                                                    person acting on his behalf for exemption from any examination on
                                                    medical grounds shall be submitted to the Vice Chancellor through
                                                    the Dean, HOD and course lecturer not later than 7 days after the
                                                    date of the examination, providing full relevant evidence (medical
                                                    certificate supplied or recognized by the Director of the University
                                                    Medical Centre/ Services)
                                                </p>
                                            </ol>
                                        </ul>
