                                        <ul>
                                            <h5>
                                                <b>DETERMINATION OF PASS, REPEAT, PROBATION AND WITHDRAWAL PERFORMANCE
                                                    PASS:</b>
                                            </h5>
                                            <ol>
                                                <p>
                                                    A person shall have passed the examination if he/she obtains pass
                                                    grade of E (1.00 point) or above in five course units minimum and
                                                    eight course Units maximum.
                                                </p>
                                            </ol>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
