                                            <h5>
                                                <b>MINOR MISCONDUCT:</b>
                                            </h5>
                                            <ol>
                                                <p>
                                                    Any act of Omission or commission involving the following: <br>
                                                    1. Physical assault on any student. <br>
                                                    2. Copying at an examination. <br>
                                                    3. Gambling within the University Community. <br>
                                                    4. Unauthorized use of another student library borrowing card. <br>
                                                    5. Possession of extraneous materials at the examination. <br>
                                                    6. Using official student position to bargain for favour from any
                                                    authority of the University. <br>
                                                    7. Drunkenness on campus during school hours.
                                                </p>
                                            </ol>
                                            <h5>
                                                <b>PENALTY FOR MINOR MISCONDUCT</b>

                                            </h5>
                                            <ol>
                                                <p>
                                                    Any student found guilty of any minor misconduct shall be rusticated
                                                    from the University for one year with cancelation of the results in
                                                    the case of examination misconduct.
                                                </p>
                                            </ol>
                                        </ul>
                                    </div>
                                </div>

