                                                <b>FINAL YEAR OF STUDY:</b>
                                            </h5>
                                            <ol>
                                                <p>
                                                    A student who fails to obtain the necessary minimum requirements for
                                                    degree may be permitted by senate to enroll for an additional period
                                                    of study not exceeding 50% of the total approved duration for
                                                    his/her programme including any probation and/or suspension of study
                                                    years but excluding a sickness period covered by medical report
                                                    approved by Senate.
                                                </p>
                                            </ol>
                                        </ul>
